Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是跟你道歉
